ar/0bfbe225dd6be69b3949f3436fa9c7d3?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:12:\"John Russell\";}s:15:\"nikolayyordanov\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:46:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nikolayyordanov\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ba7ade3c5276591a8dd38047a89f1de7?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:16:\"Nikolay Yordanov\";}s:7:\"codente\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:38:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/codente\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2da21f257e56c57525ce4402ce9bf246?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:5:\"Jamie\";}s:5:\"pross\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:36:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pross\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/df9c761356c574b3fd5042db3273e438?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:13:\"Simon Prosser\";}s:13:\"pedromendonca\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:44:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pedromendonca\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/39736018b4d3a3c544db97a780167af9?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:15:\"Pedro Mendonça\";}}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.6\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"5.4.1\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"5.6\";s:6:\"rating\";i:96;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:310;i:4;i:8;i:3;i:2;i:2;i:5;i:1;i:7;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:332;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:16;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:12;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:300000;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2020-03-27 3:45pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2014-11-04\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:107:\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/?utm_medium=bb&utm_source=plugins-admin-page&utm_campaign=plugins-admin-uri\";s:8:\"sections\";a:6:{s:11:\"description\";s:6354:\"<h4>¿Qué es The Beaver Builder Page Builder?</h4>\n<p>Beaver Builder es un flexible maquetador de páginas de arrastrar y soltar que funciona en la portada de tu web de WordPress. Seas un principiante o un profesional, te va a encantar tomar el control de tu web. Deja de escribir HTML o de pelear con confusos shortcodes. Con Beaver Builder, construir en WordPress páginas bonitas y profesionales es tan sencillo como arrastrar y soltar.</p>\n<p>Mira el vídeo de abajo o <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/go/demo?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-demo-link\" title=\"Demostración en directo de Beaver Builder\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">prueba nuestra demostración</a> ¡para verlo en acción!</p>\n<div class=\"embed-vimeo\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/122546222\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Soporte Premium</strong></p>\n<p>El equipo de Beaver Builder proporciona un soporte muy limitado en los foros de WordPress.org. Por favor, no dudes en hacer preguntas o informar de fallos, pero para un soporte <em>a tiempo</em> recomendamos la compra de una licencia de Beaver Builder.</p>\n<p>Junto con el acceso a nuestro experto equipo de soporte, en las versiones premium hay muchas características que ahorran tiempo, lo que las hace de un gran valor para cualquier usuario serio de WordPress. <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/pricing/?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-support-cta\" title=\"Soporte premium de Beaver Builder\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"><strong>Obtén hoy una licencia.</strong></a></p>\n<p>También puedes consultar nuestra <a href=\"https://kb.wpbeaverbuilder.com/\" title=\"Beaver Builder Knowledge Base\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Knowledge Base</a>, o intentar pedir ayuda a la comunidad Beaver Builder en <a href=\"http://beaver.builders/wp-repo-fb\" title=\"Beaver Builders on Facebook\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Facebook</a> o <a href=\"http://beaver.builders/wp-repo-slack\" title=\"Beaver Builders on Slack\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Slack</a>. Ten en cuenta que  todas estas personas son gente como tú que se ofrece a ayudar.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4>Únete a nuestra creciente comunidad</h4>\n<p>¡Hay una enorme colonia (<em>sí, ese es el término para un grupo de castores</em>) de «Beaver Builders» a los que les encantaría conocerte! Si tienes preguntas, un proyecto que mostrar, o te gustaría conocer y relacionarte con otros usuarios de Beaver Builder, te sentirás como en casa en el <a href=\"http://beaver.builders/wp-repo-fb\" title=\"Beaver Builders on Facebook\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">grupo de Facebook Beaver Builders</a> o en el <a href=\"http://beaver.builders/wp-repo-slack\" title=\"Beaver Builders on Slack\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">canal de Slack de Beaver Builders</a>. Ven a saludar.</p>\n<h4>Funciones de Page Builder</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Módulos de contenido: HTML, Foto, Editor de Texto, Audio, Video y Barra Lateral (sidebar).</li>\n<li>Anchura completa, composiciones basadas en columnas.</li>\n<li>Ligero y con marcado semántico para un máximo rendimiento.</li>\n<li>Fondos de filas de fotos, colores y vídeos.</li>\n<li>Estructuras adaptables, adecuadas para móviles.</li>\n<li>Añada sus propias clases CSS e IDs.</li>\n<li>Usa Shotcodes y Widgets de WordPress</li>\n<li>Funciona con páginas, entradas y tipos de contenido personalizados.</li>\n<li>Una comunidad amigable y colaborativa.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Características Premium</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Módulos adicionales: formulario de contacto, pestañas, carrusel, tabla de precios, mapa, entradas de blog, formulario de suscripción, iconos de redes sociales y mucho más.</li>\n<li>Soporte experto de nuestro equipo de soporte de primera clase.</li>\n<li>Bonitos diseños de plantillas prefabricadas.</li>\n<li>Guarda, exporta y reutiliza estructuras de página completas, filas y módulos.</li>\n<li>Crea tus propios módulos.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ven a la <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-homepage-link\" title=\"Página de inicio de Beaver Builder\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">página de inicio de Beaver Builder</a> para aprender más sobre qué pueden hacer por ti nuestras ¡características premium!</p>\n<h4>La gente REALMENTE AMA a Beaver Builder</h4>\n<p>No te limites a creer en nuestra palabra, aquí tienes algunos testimonios de usuarios y clientes satisfechos.</p>\n<p>«En pocas palabras, es el constructor de páginas en el ecosistema de WordPress. No hay un segundo cercano.» &#8211; WP Crafter</p>\n<p>«Completa libertad de diseño sin progrmar y además es totalmente adaptable». &#8211; skyboro</p>\n<p>«Fácil de usar, rápido de aprender, profundidad real del producto, gran soporte.» &#8211; David Bressler</p>\n<h4>Módulos y Widgets</h4>\n<p>Hemos cargado Beaver Builder con un flexible conjunto de módulos de contenido para ayudarte a crear impresionantes diseños y páginas de destino dentro de un intuitivo sistema de arrastrar y soltar. Beaver Builder también es compatible con los widgets y shortcodes del núcleo de WordPress y de terceros, por lo que puedes usar Beaver Builder ¡con todos tus <em>otros</em> plugins favoritos!</p>\n<h4>Un constructor de páginas para WordPress que funciona con tu tema</h4>\n<p>¡Sí, así es! Beaver Builder fue diseñado para trabajar con casi cualquier tema de WordPress. Prueba hoy Beaver Builder en tu web o considera actualizar y usar la excelente estructura de tema de Beaver Builder (disponible en los paquetes Pro y Agency) para tu próximo proyecto.</p>\n<h4>Un constructor de páginas para WordPress 100% adaptado a móviles</h4>\n<p>Cada parte de un diseño o página de destino de Beaver Builder es totalmente adaptable y se ve magnífica en cualquier tamaño de pantalla. El diseño web adaptable nunca ha sido tan fácil.</p>\n<h4>Un constructor de páginas para WordPress que está optimizado para el rendimiento</h4>\n<p>Hemos diseñado Beaver Builder para crear diseños y páginas de aterrizaje que se cargan rápidamente. Muchos constructores de páginas cargan un número impío de scripts y hojas de estilo en cada página de tu sitio. ¡Beaver Builder no! Sólo carga los activos necesarios para un diseño o página de aterrizaje determinados.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:1045:\"<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Instala Beaver Builder desde el directorio de plugins de WordPress o subiendo los archivos a tu servidor en wp-content/plugins.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Después de activar Beaver Builder, navega a la página de ajustes en Settings &gt; Page Builder para configurar los tipos de publicaciones con los que quieres que funcione.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Aparecerá una pestaña de <em>«Maquetador de página»</em> en el área de «Editar página/entrada». También aparecerá la opción <em>«Maquetador de página»</em> en la barra de administración de WordPress en la portada de tu web.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Para más información, por favor, visita nuestra <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/documentation/?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-install-kb-link\" title=\"Base de conocimiento de Beaver Builder\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">base de conocimiento</a>. Ten en cuenta que no todas las características descritas en la base de conocimiento están disponibles en esta versión del plugin Beaver Builder.</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:636:\"<p>Para información sobre el uso de Beaver Builder, por favor, visita nuestra <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/knowledge-base/?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-faq-kb-link\" title=\"Base de conocimiento de Beaver Builder\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">base de conocimiento</a>.</p>\n<p>Para preguntas generales o preguntas sobre la compra de una licencia, revisa nuestra página de <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/frequently-asked-questions/?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-faq-link\" title=\"Beaver Builder FAQs\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">preguntas frecuentes</a>.</p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:356:\"<p>Visita nuestra <a href=\"https://www.wpbeaverbuilder.com/change-logs/?utm_medium=bb-lite&amp;utm_source=repo-readme&amp;utm_campaign=repo-changelog-page\" title=\"Beaver Builder Changelog\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">página de registro de cambios</a> para obtener información actualizada sobre lo que ha estado sucediendo con el desarrollo de Beaver Builder.</p>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:1149:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1372383\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1372383\" alt=\"Iniciando Beaver Builder desde el backend.\"></a><p>Iniciando Beaver Builder desde el backend.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1372383\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1372383\" alt=\"Iniciando Beaver Builder desde la parte frontal.\"></a><p>Iniciando Beaver Builder desde la parte frontal.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1372383\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1372383\" alt=\"La interfaz de edición principal.\"></a><p>La interfaz de edición principal.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=1372383\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=1372383\" alt=\"Edición básica de texto.\"></a><p>Edición básica de texto.</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:15192:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great page builder</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kocsisagica\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/da3bf2cbb49a1140cedeaefd0eb13454?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/da3bf2cbb49a1140cedeaefd0eb13454?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kocsisagica\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kocsisagica</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">mayo 1, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great user experience and support.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin &amp; brilliant support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/marmitejim\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e8d47250940e1b4d00aea3029127b789?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e8d47250940e1b4d00aea3029127b789?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/marmitejim\" class=\"reviewer-name\">marmitejim</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">abril 24, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Hi, I usually don\'t bother writing reviews but I have to say that the support provided by this company is really fast. They don\'t bat you off with standard responses but actually look at the issue properly and discuss it with you intelligently.\n\nI use BB on all my sites now. Way, way, way better than any other page builder.\n\nKeep up the good work BB!\n\nThanks\nJ</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best Support!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nstone01\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/709d0a260b8dbc37e477fe3215e3cd06?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/709d0a260b8dbc37e477fe3215e3cd06?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nstone01\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nstone01</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">abril 22, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Not only is the product great, but the support is amazing. Thanks Jamie for all your help</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">They see mistakes that you might not</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/scaramia\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0815d34f32b04480d72672c601636bb1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0815d34f32b04480d72672c601636bb1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/scaramia\" class=\"reviewer-name\">scaramia</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">abril 10, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">...and then you can fix it, and learn something.  Win Win!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">BEST IN CLASS, PERIOD!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thegutelife\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/066c1563ac5b7af4f5b7e98833009c31?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/066c1563ac5b7af4f5b7e98833009c31?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thegutelife\" class=\"reviewer-name\">thegutelife</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">abril 7, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been using BB for 5 years and have had nothing but an exceptional experience. Their drag and drop interface is amazing, their customer support is EXACTLY what you\'re looking for- always responsive, no issue too small or too big, and they ALWAYS solve it.\n\nIf you\'re looking to really learn how to build websites or run an advertising / media / marketing agency that builds websites, BB TOTALLY is what you need.\n\nThanks again guys! You all rock!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simply great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brandontan903\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/73b8bddbf4abdb30268efe3709987a0b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/73b8bddbf4abdb30268efe3709987a0b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brandontan903\" class=\"reviewer-name\">brandontan903</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">marzo 22, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It is so great until I have no word to say</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesomely Unparalleled</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/m4cl4rkgmailcom\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0b6c9344d910f426f882bcf20fc40da5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0b6c9344d910f426f882bcf20fc40da5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/m4cl4rkgmailcom\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mc <small>(m4cl4rk@gmail.com)</small></a> el <span class=\"review-date\">marzo 5, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">When you come across a product that really resonates, you can feel how much thoughtfulness and love go into making it great and keeping it great. That\'s the feeling you get with BeaverBuilder. Not only is it among the most well-crafted systems you\'ll ever use, it\'s also one of the most delightful.\n\nNo matter the project, I look forward to using this one each and every day.\n\nI don\'t often review things, and when I do, it\'s because the product and/or service really strike me as so extraordinary, that I\'d better chip my two cents in and add my voice to the chorus of happy customers. The product and the customer service here are awesomely unparalleled. In a good way. The best way. :)\n\nThanks, Builder Team. You rock.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Invaluable</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bryan-freedman\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/46b03926f7c0569a4fa04846a428c233?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/46b03926f7c0569a4fa04846a428c233?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bryan-freedman\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Bryan Freedman</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">marzo 5, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">For beginner/wannabe web designers like me, this is a must. Makes designing pages so much easier. Great templates too. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Product and Great Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/klhall1987\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/27a47a338f432fdfd9fa2531f50401ff?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/27a47a338f432fdfd9fa2531f50401ff?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/klhall1987\" class=\"reviewer-name\">klhall1987</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">febrero 12, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This product is amazing. I seriously can\'t sing it\'s praises enough. I use it on most sites I build at this point, it makes spinning up a site super simple and their support team is incredible. They always seem to go the extra mile. If you\'re look for a page builder, this is the place start and end your search! </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Not overly impressed</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/krammig\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fb6ea68f3d897997ad1ded10271205ad?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fb6ea68f3d897997ad1ded10271205ad?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/krammig\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Krammig</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">enero 30, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Sorry people however I am not particularly impressed with this. \n\nIt looks good in the marketing blurb, and on your website, however I have tried to edit an existing site called Faded and it just does not work. \n\nBy that I mean clicking on Text to edit, or a Button, just shows actual code in the Visual view. Exactly the same in the Text view. \n\nSo unless I want to go bit by bit through code lines to change text or whatever - which I don\'t - it is pretty useless. </div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:70:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:4:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:80:\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1372383\";s:7:\"caption\";s:42:\"Iniciando Beaver Builder desde el backend.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:80:\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1372383\";s:7:\"caption\";s:48:\"Iniciando Beaver Builder desde la parte frontal.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:80:\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1372383\";s:7:\"caption\";s:34:\"La interfaz de edición principal.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:80:\"https://ps.w.org/beaver-builder-lite-version/assets/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=1372383\";s:7:\"caption\";s:26:\"Edición básica de texto.\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:14:\"beaver-builder\";s:14:\"beaver builder\";s:20:\"drag-and-drop-editor\";s:20:\"Drag And Drop editor\";s:17:\"front-end-builder\";s:17:\"front-end builder\";s:12:\"landing-page\";s:12:\"landing page\";s:12:\"page-builder\";s:12:\"page builder\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:86:{s:6:\"1.10.4\";s:77:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.10.4.zip\";s:8:\"1.10.5.1\";s:79:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.10.5.1.zip\";s:8:\"1.10.6.3\";s:79:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.10.6.3.zip\";s:8:\"1.10.6.4\";s:79:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.10.6.4.zip\";s:8:\"1.10.6.5\";s:79:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.10.6.5.zip\";s:6:\"1.10.7\";s:77:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.10.7.zip\";s:8:\"1.10.8.3\";s:79:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.10.8.3.zip\";s:6:\"1.10.9\";s:77:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.10.9.zip\";s:8:\"1.10.9.1\";s:79:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.10.9.1.zip\";s:8:\"1.10.9.2\";s:79:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.10.9.2.zip\";s:4:\"1.11\";s:75:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.11.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.6\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.3.6.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.7\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.3.7.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.8\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.3.8.zip\";s:7:\"1.3.8.1\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.3.8.1.zip\";s:7:\"1.3.8.2\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.3.8.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.9\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.3.9.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.0\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.4.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.1\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.4.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.2\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.4.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.3\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.4.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.5\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.4.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.6\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.4.6.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.8\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.4.8.zip\";s:5:\"1.5.0\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.5.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.5.3\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.5.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.5.5\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.5.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.5.6\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.5.6.zip\";s:5:\"1.5.9\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.5.9.zip\";s:7:\"1.6.0.1\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.6.0.1.zip\";s:7:\"1.6.1.1\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.6.1.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.6.2\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.6.2.zip\";s:7:\"1.6.2.1\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.6.2.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.6.4\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/beaver-builder-lite-version.1.6.4.zip\";s:7:\"1.6.4.1\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wor